title: Boom Boom Satellites - Embrace
description:
Embrace is the eighth studio album by Japanese electronic/rock duo Boom Boom Satellites. Released on January 9, 2013. Songs on the album include their single "Broken Mirror", "Drifter", which was used in Sony's Xperia commercials, and "Another Perfect Day", featured in the credits of Starship Troopers: Invasion.
